Package: SolelyData
Type: Package
Title: An Intuitive Data Analysis Toolkit for R Beginners
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Maisha", "Kasole", email = "maisha.kasole@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <maisha.kasole@gmail.com>
Description: SolelyData provides user-friendly tools and workflows for cleaning, analyzing, 
    and visualizing raw datasets. It is specifically designed with erroneous datasets in mind, 
    offering tailored functionalities to address common challenges in data handling
    and exploration. Ideal for beginners to R, this package emphasizes simplicity and effectiveness.
